FSRepo is a Liferay 6.1 Hook for mapping existing local file system into Liferay as a new Documents & Media repository.

Copyright (c) 2012 Tomáš Polešovský

Based on a brainstorming idea with Aleš Rybák when talking about Liferay Sync!

Documentation
=============
Please see wiki: https://github.com/topolik/FSRepo/wiki

Installation
------------
Download from https://github.com/topolik/FSRepo/downloads and copy into deploy directory

Local Build & Deploy
--------------------
Edit pom.xml and define correct location for: <liferay.auto.deploy.dir>

Call `mvn clean package liferay:deploy'

